name: Vault 7 - by Dr Abstract
description:
BEFORE Escape Rooms there was Vault 7 - the interface challenge to break into a vault - designed by MysteryMind, Dr Abstract. Watch for the prequel, Vault 6 - dropping sometime soon! Who knows, with enough interest, we would love to make Vault 8 where you have to break out of the vault... 

Dr Abstract is the Founder of ZIM at https://zimjs.com where you can make interactive NFTs and more https://zimjs.com/nft. Join the GadgetMinters if making NFT Gadgets is your thing! We would love to meet you https://zimjs.com/gadgetminters

Until then, collect this seminal example of ZIM created in ZIM ONE - we have since gone through DUO, TRI, 4TH, VEE, SIX, HEP, OCT, NIO, TEN, and CAT The current version of ZIM is ZIM NFT - ZIM is an NFT!
